{"tid":2081300,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅致光料失業率將升至6%","createTime":"2020-06-27T06:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T18:54:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9c7b130469702482254901b10be0dce6e7f1f3b8","tid":2081300,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:11:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534393-20200627.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534393-20200627.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=3976fb97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534393-20200627.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8541c42a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534393-20200627.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光說，預計未來一段時間，本港失業率會維持5%至6%的水平，不會在短時間內下降，相信到7月份公布4至6月平均失業率，會超過6%。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光出席一個電台節目時又說，現時全球經濟已經進入衰退，甚至差不多達到經濟蕭條的情況，對本港失業情況並不樂觀，預計未來幾年都不會達到失業率少於3%的「全民就業」水平。<br />\n<br />\n另外，羅致光說，在疫情下不鼓勵外僱來港，如果政府安排或資助來港的外傭入住酒店檢疫，變相是鼓勵她們來港，對本港的防疫工作造成很大負擔。"},{"pid":"398e63fe3a95835044f09b4fa6a226d93b13fed6","tid":2081300,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:12:03.000Z","msg":"樓市：無影響"},{"pid":"c4282b2d28be9aba550831beddae8e5b7d6107dd","tid":2081300,"uid":171611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"398e63fe3a95835044f09b4fa6a226d93b13fed6","tid":2081300,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:12:03.000Z","msg":"樓市：無影響"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"升6%"},{"pid":"19529d99df19e132657a6bb0818148896435e42b","tid":2081300,"uid":289995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"398e63fe3a95835044f09b4fa6a226d93b13fed6","tid":2081300,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:12:03.000Z","msg":